|YKOYour blood oath gives you several abilities related to the person you
have sworn the oath with.  Available commands are:
 
|YKBotell|BKB:    |CKBThis allows you to send a message over your oath line.  It is
          essentially a free tell.
 
|YKBoemote|BKB:   |CKBWhen given with <msg> it will display <yourname> <msg>.  If you
          are Brunhilda and you type oemote "is fighting an orc" then the
          person you are sworn to will see 'Brunhilda is fighting an orc'.
 
|YKBohist|BKB:    |CKBThis lists the past 15 messages on the oath channel.

|YKBolook|BKB:    |CKBThis ability will allow one oath taker to see where the other is
          located.  It costs a nominal (5) amount of spell points to use.
 
|YKBoinspire|BKB: |CKBThis may only be performed when both blood oath takers are in
          the same room.  It will inspire you, adding to your combat abilities
          and your statistics for a time.
 
|YKBrenounce|BKB: |CKBIf you 'renounce oath' your blood oath will be cancelled.  You will
          suffer the penalties for failure to uphold your oath and in addition
          will lose respect and be marked as an oathbreaker.  You may remove
          the oathbreaker status by swearing a new oath, but must earn the
          lost respect back yourself.  Do not take oath renunciation lightly.
